HEADWORD: Crack-brained
<hw>Crack"-brained`</hw></mhw>
<pr>(-br⟦amac⟧nd`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having an impaired
intellect; whimsical; extremely foolish; crazy; <as>as,
<ex>crackbrained</ex> notions</as>.</def> <rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> idiotic.</syn>⟦br⟧
